---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const lastVerified = '2026-04-29 14:00 ET';
---

<Base
  title="Status — Ringdocket"
  description="Ringdocket system status. Block list, worker, dashboard, and ingest pipeline operational."
>
  <main class="prose-page">
    <p class="kicker mono">System status</p>
    <h1>All systems operational.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Real-time monitoring is deferred to Phase 5. This page reflects
      manually-verified state. If something looks wrong from where you sit,
      email <a href="mailto:support@ringdocket.com">support@ringdocket.com</a>
      and we will look immediately.
    </p>

    <section class="status-list">
      <div class="row">
        <span class="dot ok"></span>
        <div class="row-body">
          <p class="row-name">Public block list</p>
          <p class="row-meta mono">blocklist.ringdocket.com/current.json &middot; verified {lastVerified}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="status-tag ok mono">operational</span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <span class="dot ok"></span>
        <div class="row-body">
          <p class="row-name">API worker</p>
          <p class="row-meta mono">ringdocket-worker.bmangum1.workers.dev/api/health &middot; verified {lastVerified}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="status-tag ok mono">operational</span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <span class="dot ok"></span>
        <div class="row-body">
          <p class="row-name">Web dashboard</p>
          <p class="row-meta mono">app.ringdocket.com/app/home &middot; verified {lastVerified}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="status-tag ok mono">operational</span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <span class="dot ok"></span>
        <div class="row-body">
          <p class="row-name">FTC ingest cron</p>
          <p class="row-meta mono">last successful run 2026-04-29 06:00 UTC &middot; 86,519 complaints in store</p>
        </div>
        <span class="status-tag ok mono">operational</span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <span class="dot ok"></span>
        <div class="row-body">
          <p class="row-name">Auth (Supabase magic-link)</p>
          <p class="row-meta mono">verified {lastVerified}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="status-tag ok mono">operational</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <h2>Sources of truth</h2>
    <ul class="links">
      <li>
        <a href="https://blocklist.ringdocket.com/current.json" rel="noopener">
          blocklist.ringdocket.com/current.json
        </a>
        &mdash; the live, public block list. If this 200s with valid JSON, distribution is healthy.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://ringdocket-worker.bmangum1.workers.dev/api/health" rel="noopener">
          ringdocket-worker.bmangum1.workers.dev/api/health
        </a>
        &mdash; worker health probe. If this 200s, the API plane is up.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://app.ringdocket.com/app/home" rel="noopener">
          app.ringdocket.com/app/home
        </a>
        &mdash; web dashboard. Sign in to confirm authenticated routes resolve.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="footnote">
      A real status backend &mdash; with synthetic checks, uptime history, and
      incident timelines &mdash; is on the Phase 5 roadmap. Until then, this
      page is updated by hand whenever the underlying state changes.
    </p>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-page {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem) 5rem;
  }
  .kicker {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--signal-corroborated);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque';
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 2.875rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque';
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: 'Newsreader';
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .lead a {
    color: var(--ink-primary);
  }
  .status-list {
    background: var(--surface-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-subtle);
  }
  .row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 0.625rem;
    height: 0.625rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .dot.ok {
    background: var(--signal-corroborated);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--signal-corroborated) 18%, transparent);
  }
  .row-name {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight';
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .row-meta {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--ink-byline);
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
  }
  .status-tag.ok {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--signal-corroborated);
  }
  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Newsreader';
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }
  .links li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule-subtle);
  }
  .links li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .links a {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono';
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .footnote {
    font-family: 'Newsreader';
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--ink-byline);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
</style>
